to install mongodb you should install it from this website
https://www.mongodb.com/download-center

after you install it and setup the mongodb open the cmd panel
on "bin" file and type "mongod" to run the database

to make sure that the mongodb is working go to services
and search for mongodb and you must see it running

after that you can download mongodb compass to open and see
the data bases

now open your project on your IDE , editor or cmd and install the packages
by typing:-
npm install mongodb
npm install mongod
npm install mongoose

and have fun with mongo ;)
